com.evite.qv.webservice
Class QVWebServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
  com.evite.qv.webservice.QVWebServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
QVWebService, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware
public class QVWebServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements QVWebService, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware

QVWebserviceImpl provides functionality for creating/retrieving Quickvite-type events. It is meant to be used as an externally facing API to allow for 3rd party integration. It basically just delegates to the QVWebserviceManager after checking credentials

Version:
$Id: QVWebServiceImpl.java,v 1.12.2.3 2007/11/27 03:53:52 krishna Exp $
